*Obzira* na to da li će biti dovoljno vremena, odlučili smo da putujemo. (Regardless of whether there is enough time, we decided to travel.)

Ne zanima me *obzira* na tvoj stav. (I don't care about your attitude.)

*Obzira* se na to koliko je teško, moraš da nastaviš. (Regardless of how difficult it is, you must continue.)

Nismo imali dovoljno vremena, ali nismo se obazirali na to. (We didn't have enough time, but we didn't take that into account.)

Nisam se obazirala *obzira* na njegove priče. (I didn't pay attention to his stories.)